\newlabel{fig:overview-slide}{{1}{1}{The state-of-the-art \methodname \ Model: A transformer hypernetwork uses self attention to process a steering prompt and uses a cross attention module to read from the residual stream of a base LM run on a second prompt. The hypernetwork outputs a steering vector that is added to the base LM residual stream.\relax }{figure.caption.1}{}}
